{"tid":1603357,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[十一文宣] 諗下點樣幫中共贈慶","createTime":"2019-09-29T16:09:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T16:14:19.000Z","uid":145021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3db4d5864f828fd7c1dd225222581749f890894d","tid":1603357,"uid":145021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:09:37.000Z","msg":"不過列晒呢啲事件出嚟幫人認識下近代中國史？<br />\n<br />\n中共建政七十周年大事記<br />\n<br />\n1950-1953 土地改革運動（鬥地主）<br />\n死亡人數：估計200至300萬<br />\n<br />\n1957、1959 反右運動、反右傾運動<br />\n影響：估計300多萬人被「打」成右派，目的在整肅異己，剷除反對聲音，埋下大躍進及文革的伏線<br />\n<br />\n1958 除四害、打麻雀運動<br />\n影響：嚴重破壞生態平衡，糧食嚴重欠收<br />\n<br />\n1958-1960 大躍進<br />\n影響：農牧業產品大幅減產，直接導致大饑荒<br />\n<br />\n1959-1961 三年大饑荒<br />\n死亡人數：估計1,650萬至4,300萬<br />\n<br />\n1950-1959 吞併西藏<br />\n過程：武力威嚇&mdash;＞偽造條約&mdash;＞土地改革&mdash;＞完全吞併<br />\n<br />\n1966-1976 文化大革命（十年浩劫）<br />\n影響：摧毀文明，道德淪喪<br />\n受迫害人數：至少一億<br />\n死亡人數：至少三百萬<br />\n<br />\n1989 六四事件<br />\n死亡人數：數千<br />\n影響：中國再無反對聲音，黨國路線無可逆轉<br />\n<br />\n1991 五一六協定<br />\n內容：主動放棄索回北方100多萬平方公里國土的權利，變相承認沙俄同滿清簽訂的不平等條約<br />\n<br />\nSource：自己睇wiki"},{"pid":"08637f3e884fd103e44794d1b49adf28847990ba","tid":1603357,"uid":145021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HQohHjC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHQohHjC.gif&h=c9733fc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a4641de928cd0dd119e62847f3c38be751fc64f","tid":1603357,"uid":145021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SJegXS1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSJegXS1.jpg&h=e863dd5c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"264ae77e1fd23d4a29dc24c233f87642920ebbbb","tid":1603357,"uid":145021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:11:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cg3hHj0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A